{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1f7f21e16","title":"给毛岸英、毛岸青的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13be76bf2a","index":0,"year":1939,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"a1f7f21e16"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4f30dcfd83","type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸英、毛岸青的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"},{"id":"1f6286f31b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年8月26日）岸英岸青二儿：你们上次信收到了，十分欢喜你们近来好否？有进步香？我还好，也看了一点书，但不多，心里觉得很不满足，不如你们是专门学习的时候为你们及所有小同志，托林伯渠老同志买了一批书，口寄给你们，不知收到否？来信告我。下次再写祝你们发展，向上，愉快！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"},{"id":"e07fb8a2a3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"},{"id":"cffe75e250","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三九年八月二十六日[1]林伯渠，当时是中国共产党驻西安的代表。毛泽东托林伯乘买了一北书客给在英斯科学习的孩子们，可惜这批书在邮途中丢关了常老汽有院hm你们也本元：有也的我好，邮个生美，化号衣爱得依一的走，师传净川海外中候。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"},{"id":"de2339e4f7","type":"paragraph","text":"为你公场小能件所购点冠个抢第，常体你小的买代。你屏。预你欢m","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"},{"id":"8fcf2fcc3d","type":"paragraph","text":"hin人科奖毛泽东致毛岸英、毛岸青信的手稿","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16"}],"page":{"id":"808d3acc97","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a1f7f21e16","start":511,"end":512}}}},"__N_SSG":true}